<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شَيْبَةَ، <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5774">وَابْنُ نُمَيْرٍ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3689">وَأَبُو سَعِيدٍ الْأَشَجُّ </a>قَالُوا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6792">وَكِيعٌ </a>. <span class="c2">(ح)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5820">أَبُو كُرَيْبٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5577">أَبُو مُعَاوِيَةَ </a>، كِلَاهُمَا عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ نَحْوَهُ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>